---

<section id="nosotros" class="py-24 relative bg-black overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-green-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Side: Mission Card -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-600 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-green-500"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Nuestra Misión</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Impulsar el crecimiento profesional de cada estudiante mediante el <span
              class="text-green-400 font-medium">aprendizaje práctico</span
            > y la colaboración en proyectos de alto impacto.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Side: Content -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Más que código, somos <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-emerald-600"
            >Comunidad</span
          >
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8">
          En Unicode, no solo escribimos líneas de código; construimos
          soluciones, forjamos amistades y creamos el futuro de la tecnología en
          nuestra universidad.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div
              class="mt-1 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 ring-1 ring-green-500/20"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="w-4 h-4"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 001.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 01-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 01-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 01-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.823 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 10-7.517 0c.85.493 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Innovación Constante</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-400">
                Exploramos las últimas tecnologías y tendencias del mercado
                global.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div
              class="mt-1 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 ring-1 ring-green-500/20"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="w-4 h-4"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">
                Mentoria y Networking
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-400">
                Conecta con expertos y egresados líderes en la industria tech.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
